ds_priority_add: With this function you can add a value (either a real number or a string) to a priority queue, at the same time assigning it a priority value.
The id of the priority queue to add to.
The value to add to the priority queue.

The above code adds a script function to the priority queue indexed in the variable "ai_priority" and assigns it a priority of 5.
